    "note_tweet": {
      "entities": {},
      "text": "理性分析，我认为习近平和金正恩是最难倒台的，因为其对内洗脑过于严重，统治的基本盘很扎实。假如川普今天斩首了习或金，大部分民众会愤怒地咒骂川普，叫嚣着对美开战，而非像委内瑞拉、伊朗人那样欢呼雀跃。\nA rational analysis: I believe Xi Jinping and Kim Jong-un are the most difficult to overthrow, because their internal brainwashing is too severe, and the basic foundation of their rule is very solid. If Trump were to assassinate Xi or Kim today, most people would angrily curse Trump, clamoring for war against the US, rather than cheering and rejoicing like the people in Venezuela and Iran."
    },
